ISLAMABAD, Mar 21 (APP):President Islamic Development Bank (IDB), Mohammad Sulaiman Al Jasser arrived here on Monday morning to attend 48th session of the OIC Council of Foreign Ministers.
He was warmly welcomed by Minister of State for Information and Broadcasting Farrukh Habib and Special Representative on Religious Harmony Muhammad Tahir Ashrafi.
